prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous birthday card scene, with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, paper texture, and organic paint bleeds. The central focus is a cartoon illustration of two specific people. On the left is Lao Lao, a young woman of East Asian descent in her early 20s with long, straight dark brown hair parted on the side, wearing thin round metal-framed glasses, and a light blue crewneck sweatshirt with a circular "ROCKY MO...IDGE" logo. She has a warm, happy smile with her arms crossed. Behind her and embracing her is Jordan, a young man of Southeast Asian descent in his early 20s with short, textured black hair. He wears a tan hoodie and has a wide, cheerful, and very happy smile. The background is a simple, light wash of pastel colors with whimsical watercolor splatters and drips in bright, festive hues like yellow, pink, and teal, giving it a celebratory and lighthearted feel. Centered in the middle of the card, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to the best Lao Lao!".

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
